data.description: ***SELLER OFFERING 10k TOWARDS CLOSING COSTS OR RATE BUY DOWN*** This beautiful 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom home sits on a serene 1-acre  lot. It has a 50-year metal roof, hardwood floors throughout the common areas, elegant crown molding, and granite countertops in the kitchen. There is a two-car basement garage and it has front and back porches for your relaxation.  There is also 2.9 acres that is being sold separately or can be purchased with this property.  This house is located approximately 10 minutes from the south Huntsville area.
